title: Jarvan Space Program

replies.body: Funny enough, the space program can be done by anyone with a knock up. I've seen videos of it happening to people hit by a Sejuani charge, Vel'Koz e, Cho q... Its been a bug for a really long time that Riot hasn't fixed yet.
Yesterday I had a melee minion stuck on bot turret, it wouldn't/couldn't move form the turret...
Earlier in my game the game pathed me through a cannon minion, froze, and forced closed.
